Description: Toodyay Rd section over Jane Brook bridge is poorly lit, the road comes to a bend after the rest-bay stop area (which is also in poor condition as gravel road surface), this road area after Chapel Farm until Talbot Road has no street lighting, thus oncoming traffic usually blind you with their high-beam lights on the bend. Additionally the road surface needs improvement, as cracks are re-appearing at the road-bridge pass-over.
